{
  "description": "A breathtaking aerial view captures a vibrant sunset over a sprawling coastal city and expansive bay. The sun is a brilliant orange orb partially obscured by layers of cloud, casting a warm, golden glow across the scene. The clouds themselves are dramatically lit with shades of orange, red, and subtle pink, creating a picturesque and fiery sky. Below, the city sprawls with a network of buildings and streets, appearing as a darker mass against the luminous backdrop. A large bay stretches into the distance, dotted with boats and connected by a long bridge. The overall composition conveys a sense of vastness, tranquility, and natural beauty.",
